<br>
I didn't do that. I became fustrated and got stupid. That is NOT how conflict driven RP should be conducted, as you can see the result from it, it ended very poorly, even with someone as thickskinned as Sarhea. Thats when I really began to realize my mistakes and where I was going wrong with alot of things.<br>
<br>
I've distanced myself from the game more, and taken it less seriously and less personally.<br>
<br>
THAT is the key right there. Do NOT take it to heart. Its just a game, nothing here is personal. Once you take something personally, you're screwed and you'll be seeing your name on the soapbox, either posting or on the recieving end of a complaint on how your charrie is being racist or some other bullshit that YOU REALLY DONT NEED. I know, I've been there twice already.<br>
<br>
And I don't plan on making a third trip. Since then, my conflicts have been much better, all sides enjoy the interactions, and all is going well. But its not just the 'attackee' that shouldn't take it personally, the attacker has to watch him/her self and ensure that they have the proper distance emotionally from the game so that IRL emotions do not get intertwined within. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125476" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.studioeternity.com/EverquestFV/Shinsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=3907.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=3907.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=3907.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=3907.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a> <b>5</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=3907.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=3907.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3907.topic&index=84><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=3907.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.su